## `${node_pkg}`

This package only contains one platform binary for [`@smbcloud/cli`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@smbcloud/cli).
Do not install it directly.

Install the main package instead:

```sh
npm install -g @smbcloud/cli
```

The main package picks the right binary for your platform.

